{"tid":1147271,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好再俾我估中啲咩","createTime":"2019-05-09T18:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T05:14:58.000Z","uid":59569,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48c0ceb7171ab1848719b8f059fdcfeaeaa456f7","tid":1147271,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T18:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好難先好返<br />\n點解人嘅好奇心可以咁強<br />\n咩都要知 知完又唔開心喎"},{"pid":"c9e4b5a80fbca0a1718b5184ede10ff1a6231437","tid":1147271,"uid":141901,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T18:42:41.000Z","msg":"你覺得呢個世界會點，你嘅信念會改變你嘅行為，從而最後跟住你所想嘅方向走，亦即係比你估中"},{"pid":"2feb28ef41e061c48ea2e8b64102dbcd9acac556","tid":1147271,"uid":242403,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T18:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71ff2ba8c28f1e9090d3e0fe46b5ddac30913c3","tid":1147271,"uid":59569,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"c9e4b5a80fbca0a1718b5184ede10ff1a6231437","tid":1147271,"uid":141901,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T18:42:41.000Z","msg":"你覺得呢個世界會點，你嘅信念會改變你嘅行為，從而最後跟住你所想嘅方向走，亦即係比你估中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T19:44:57.000Z","msg":"以前細過會成日想得到一種能力<br />\n就係可以接觸完一個人或物就知道曾經過會發生啲咩<br />\n一直都覺得好好用<br />\n但愈嚟愈大 <br />\n就發覺呢種能力根本害緊自己<br />\n<br />\n好多時唔知咁多嘅話會輕鬆好多<br />\n一個個人哋收埋好嘅秘密都俾自己破解到<br />\n最抵死係一講就中 <br />\n對方死雞撐飯蓋種態度仲令自己討厭<br />\n<br />\n點解永遠紙都包唔住火<br />\n知咁多又點 <br />\n人哋唔想俾你知先係重點<br />\n聰明反被聰明誤"},{"pid":"f0b418132720874e05a7fb65f69ee9cf0b258cb2","tid":1147271,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T19:46:05.000Z","msg":"有一日唔記得帶個護符出街<br />\n成日都神不守舍咁<br />\n點解"},{"pid":"5f6fd2c2bfec98f3